in this great campaign"

1635
02:37:01,421 --> 02:37:04,840
"to rid the world
of tyranny and oppression."

1636
02:37:04,924 --> 02:37:08,177
"I take great pleasure in joining
the Secretary of War,"

1637
02:37:08,345 --> 02:37:10,429
