coming back here.

1661
02:39:14,804 --> 02:39:18,223
Every day I think about
what you said to me

1662
02:39:18,308 --> 02:39:20,434
that day on the bridge.

1663
02:39:22,312 --> 02:39:25,773
And I've tried to live my life
the best I could.

1664
02:39:26,858 --> 02:39:29,276
